			"name":"Description",
			"type":"feature",
			"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>A cloud of shimmering black energy suddenly flares above the blood-red altar, a shrieking roar rising as it advances.</i></p><p><b>Hazard:</b> The entropic nexus is a magically created gate to the Far Realm. It devours creatures, then spits them back out as horrid abominations. The entropic nexus fills an area 3 squares on a side.</p>",
					"chat":"",
					"unidentified":""
